                    <comment id="12381254" author="oglueck" created="Fri, 21 Nov 2003 16:30:40 +0000"  >I&amp;#39;ll take care of that immediately.</comment>
                    <comment id="12381255" author="oglueck" created="Fri, 21 Nov 2003 17:13:21 +0000"  >Created an attachment (id=9225)&lt;br/&gt;
Proposed fix (patch against src/)&lt;br/&gt;
</comment>
                    <comment id="12381256" author="oglueck" created="Fri, 21 Nov 2003 17:16:38 +0000"  >The patch changes the behaviour to suppress out optional fields that are not&lt;br/&gt;
present.&lt;br/&gt;
DigestScheme now only accepts a challenge if all fields required by RFC 2617 are&lt;br/&gt;
present. Otherwise an exception is thrown. Test cases have been updated&lt;br/&gt;
accordingly. The test case also makes sure there is not &amp;quot;null&amp;quot; string in the&lt;br/&gt;
response.&lt;br/&gt;
Please review.</comment>
                    <comment id="12381257" author="olegk" created="Sat, 22 Nov 2003 20:09:04 +0000"  >The patch looks good to me. &lt;br/&gt;
